data.title: Celebrity birthdays for the week of Dec. 27-Jan. 2
data.meta_description: Celebrity birthdays for the week of Dec. 27-Jan. 2: Dec. 27: Actor John Amos (“The West Wing,” “Roots”) is 81. Guitarist Mick Jones of Foreigner is 76.
